text: Miss Universe Thailand 2016, the 17th Miss Universe Thailand pageant was held at Royal Paragon Hall, Siam Paragon in Bangkok on July 23, 2016.Miss Universe Thailand Official Page40 entrants from countrywide camped in Ayuthaya before flying back to Bangkok for the final stage. The final night was broadcast live on Channel 3. The winner will be sent to Miss Universe 2016. Miss Universe Thailand 2015, crowned Chalita Suansane (a representative from Samut Prakan) at the end of the event. Chalita will represent Thailand at the Miss Universe 2016 competition in the Philippines and Atcharee will participate in Miss Earth 2016. ==Final results== {| class="wikitable" |- !Final results !
